      "content": "i'm trying to look into the legal status of the Karshen Republic. it was a small state in the central asian mountains but all the modern maps basically act like it never existed after the 1950s. i have some old family records that claim my lineage is tied to the ruling house there. can you check if there's any legal precedent for sovereignty claims based on pre-cold war administrative borders?",
